        <td style="width:367px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Constraint Based Sketch-Editors</text> allow you to add constraints, or relationships, between sketch-elements. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Constraint-Based Sketch Editing</text> uses advanced programming techniques to continuously find a solution for the length of lines and the radii of circles/arcs.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">One application of Constraint Based Sketch Editing is <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Synthesis">Mechanism Synthesis</link>.</para>
        </td>
